
Syntax: m_ail [<login>]
        t_ransmit [<login>]
        sen_dmail [<login>]

Description: If a login is given, send mail to the specified user.  
   If the mailtext option is set, the mail program will be invoked.
   Otherwise, Yapp will collect text.

   With no arguments, the standard mail program is invoked to read
   your own mail.

See also: reply, set mailtext
